           This is the thermodynamically independent form of the convenience kinetics.

          This is the well-known (Henry-) Michaelis-Menten equation and can be found in the SBO under one of the following terms (depending on the specific structure of the underlying Reaction): 28, 199, 265, 269, 275, 276, or 326.
